sentences.sentence: For RISC processer, clock-gating can reduce power by 18.8%.
sentences.translation: 对于risc微处理器，门控时钟技术可以降低功耗18.8%。

sentences.sentence: The NC code generated by software post-processer can be used to complete the high speed machining of mould.
sentences.translation: 利用软件的后置处理功能得到了NC代码，并使用高速加工技术完成了模具的高速切削加工。

sentences.sentence: The FFT processer adopts the pipeline and parallel technology and can complete 64 points FFT computation in 64 clocks. It is able to meet the need of OFDM system.
sentences.translation: 本文设计的FFT处理器采用流水线和并行处理技术，在64个时钟周期完成64点复数定点FFT运算，可以满足OFDM系统的需要。
